Package io.github.tomaso2468.rpgonline.net

A package for handling multiplayer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Client
    An interface representing an instance of the game client's connection with the server.
    Connection
    An interface for a 2-way network connections.
    HeatAffected
    Indicates that the heat effect is supported in this client.
    PacketType
    An interface defining a packet type for a packet.
    Server
    An interface representing a server.
    TickBased
    An interface for systems based on a constant tick rate.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AESSecurityCap
    A system for setting up key exchange for AES.
    BasicPacketConnection
    A connection that uses TCP over IP to send data.
    LocalConnectionGenerator
    A class for generating local connections for use without the need for an internet connection or IO.
    ServerManager
    A class for managing currently running server and client instances.
    SingleCipherInputStream Deprecated
    SingleCipherOutputStream Deprecated
    SocketClientConnection
    A client connection that connects to a server and uses java serialisation for IO.
    SocketServerConnection
    A server connection that connects to a client and uses java serialisation for IO.
